message: The key to success is the 'vial' tool. Use 'vial' on a single, raw solid ingredient (e.g., mandrake root, unicorn horn, sunstone, mushroom) to create positive-value liquid extracts (value 30). message: To get a perfect score, always start by using the 'vial' tool on both a solid magical ingredient and a solid mundane ingredient. This creates two different liquid extracts, each worth 30 points. Then, combine these two extracts (the magical liquid and the mundane liquid) to create an item worth 100 points. Be careful with other combinations or the 'filter' tool, as they often result in negative values.
